headline: DTE Energy Company announces pricing of 2025 Series H 6.25% junior subordinated debentures
summary: DTE Energy Company (NYSE: DTE) announced today that it has priced its offering of $600 million aggregate principal amount 2025 Series H 6.25% Junior Subordinated Debentures due Oct. 1, 2085.

headline: Morgan Stanley Raises PT on DTE Energy (DTE) Stock
